  "english": [
    "From when does one recite Shema in the morning? From when one can distinguish between blue and white.",
    "Rabbi Eliezer says: Between blue and leek-green, and one completes it before sunrise.",
    "Rabbi Yehoshua says: Until three hours of the day, for such is the way of kings to rise at three hours."
  ]
